{"tid":500479,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"即將步入2018年 小欣姐肯帶爆足一周回歸未？","createTime":"2017-12-15T20:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T02:59:44.000Z","uid":152123,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"934515b1f6e835ddfd9478e8bbf135fed68075a1","tid":500479,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T20:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/20120930100618675.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F10%2F20120930100618675.jpeg&h=23d0facc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n同大家「回帶」一下查小欣喺2012年同與無綫合作，主持節目《爆足一周》，不過節目出街只有四集，並喺第四集尾聲時候，查小欣親自宣布會虛心聆聽觀眾意見，徹底檢討，調整節目內容，在2013年初再與大家見面，即變相宣布節目遭即時腰斬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2015年節目推介<br />\n<br />\n呢件事一直成為網民經常回帶事件，2013年過去，網民周不時在討論區開帖文，討論何時會喺電視再見到查小欣，可惜嚟到2014年依然無影；到最近，微博有網友將2015年節目巡禮的節目詳盡列出，網民關心的竟然是《爆足一周》有冇得重現天日。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有網民更因此大鬧TVB可恥，仲留言話︰「還我爆足一周！還我查小欣！」更形容為「香港史上最大宗走數案件」。</strong></span>而喺2015年節目巡禮節目表上，有網友發現TVB的「高清劇場」及「週末外購劇」，均出現兩套有線已播過的外購劇集《奇皇后》同《神的禮物》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在2012年10月底第四集播出之前，另一主持人莊思敏在微博上說「今晚10點#爆足一週#。。。保証你，今晚有嘢爆，唔睇就後悔嘞。。」[17]最終，在第四集的尾聲，查小欣親自宣布會虛心聆聽觀眾意見，徹底檢討，調整節目內容，在2013年初再與大家見面，即變相宣布節目遭即時腰斬，而到了2013年初，《爆足一周》也沒有任何復播的消息，可見此節目已壽終正寢。《爆足一周》原定製作13集，現在僅得4集便叫停，被指是最「短命」節目之一。網民對無綫從善如流將節目腰斬感高興，又對節目及查小欣強烈恥笑。[18]另外，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>網民對節目結束後莊思敏在「熄咪」後直接問「係咪即係腰斬呀？」及之後各主持的「O嘴」</strong></span>表情加以討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.next.nextmedia.com/images/next-photos/NextMag/1182/640pixfolder/E1182_179_tvb003.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.next.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fnext-photos%2FNextMag%2F1182%2F640pixfolder%2FE1182_179_tvb003.jpg&h=f0130fde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.next.nextmedia.com/images/next-photos/NextMag/1182/640pixfolder/E1182_179_tvb002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.next.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fnext-photos%2FNextMag%2F1182%2F640pixfolder%2FE1182_179_tvb002.jpg&h=3cb90f40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57e5086bcd495d219c7f7fac4754ef5db64778e3","tid":500479,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T20:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a4b6af8e8ce6318553ae40c92bee0c5e2cc232","tid":500479,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T21:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d144b52d916d1b8810fbf9b470071901a2c87a","tid":500479,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T22:53:13.000Z","msg":"幾時同我地見面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小欣姐"},{"pid":"ee0ff8d278222d45a804e690aee87c7720018ee2","tid":500479,"uid":42187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T23:06:03.000Z","msg":"走數真女子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8dc8ef75a88863f933f2493d8d78cf3c120281a","tid":500479,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T23:11:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時同我地見面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小欣姐</blockquote><br />\n好想知道更多爆料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7626bf4876bec3e6a369531e9d8d87f8e83c5db5","tid":500479,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:43:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>走數真女子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p